    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://mehlimabookden.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://mehlimabookden.com/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am Mehkan Mehedi, a contemporary poet and writer, known for my nostalgic and emotionally resonant style. Through Mehlima Bookden I explore nostalgic pieces, short stories, and free-hand poems inspired by emotions, memories, and the queit beauty of everyday life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I write what remains in the heart - moments often left unspoken, yet deeply felt. My words are shaped by fleeting feelings, late-night thoughts, and the warmth of memories that refuse to fade.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
